{"tid":326724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港女泰國踩單車 涉衝紅燈遭電單車撞倒傷頭","createTime":"2017-07-18T08:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T12:29:08.000Z","uid":10292,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"29b6be42b78a37f0db6d39d1e366ee7fb139c9db","tid":326724,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:33:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170718/s00001/1500361552125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170718%2Fs00001%2F1500361552125&d=fvcGqjQedSXq82cD5WSJ7pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=265842c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170718%2Fs00001%2F1500361552125&h=20fc1600\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170718/s00001/1500361552125</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名香港女子與友人在泰國踩單車旅遊期間，被電單車撞倒，頭部受傷送院治療，據報女子當時涉衝紅燈。<br />\n<br />\n《泰國世界日報》報道，該名香港女遊客今早在來興府美索縣，與友人踩單車看風景，其間在一個十字路口遭電單車撞倒，頭部受傷倒臥地上，救護人員到場將她送院救治。<br />\n<br />\n警方向傷者同行友人查問，獲悉兩人邊踩單車邊聊天，沒有留意路口的紅綠燈，兩人衝紅燈引致事故。<br />\n<br />\n（泰國世界日報）<br />\n<br />\n又柒出國際"},{"pid":"a5e1f84069bd728de87480e3c7a4954bd74aeb9f","tid":326724,"uid":31757,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:45:24.000Z","msg":"屌原來唔止車，女人連單車都出事"},{"pid":"778bc183193768da73f85e3cebdc721575e61a66","tid":326724,"uid":70092,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:51:02.000Z","msg":"1 正評 = 1 抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d13090098d8c4e79e28d09aab4b22a27d69070d","tid":326724,"uid":86893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:51:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌原來唔止車，女人連單<span style=\"color: red;\">車</span>都出事</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2159a1669a5ba8b750e779613b22c351783eec",